load ../seam-crossing.maude

--- Hazard demonstrated: the naive crosser folds a re-delivered command
--- twice -- duplicate facts in whip's log from one admitted decision.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SEAM-CROSSING :
  naive admitted(c1) deliver(c1) deliver(c1)
  =>* fact(c1) fact(c1) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Hazard demonstrated: the naive crosser folds an UNADMITTED command --
--- the authority bypass.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SEAM-CROSSING :
  naive deliver(c2)
  =>* fact(c2) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: under the sound crosser, at-least-once delivery folds exactly
--- once -- two facts for one command are unreachable.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SEAM-CROSSING :
  sound admitted(c1) deliver(c1) deliver(c1)
  =>* fact(c1) fact(c1) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: an unadmitted command never crosses.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SEAM-CROSSING :
  sound deliver(c2)
  =>* fact(c2) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Coverage: an admitted command crosses, and the duplicate arrival is
--- absorbed by the recorded crossing.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SEAM-CROSSING :
  sound admitted(c1) deliver(c1) deliver(c1)
  =>* fact(c1) crossed(c1) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Coverage: distinct admitted commands each fold once.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-SEAM-CROSSING :
  sound admitted(c1) admitted(c2) deliver(c1) deliver(c2)
  =>* fact(c1) fact(c2) RESIDUAL:Cfg .
